						<div class="postbody">The PPU register addresses have common names listed here: <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_registers" class="postlink">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_registers</a>
<br />
<br />I haven't seen names for the $4000 series registers.
<br />
<br />I think people might forego the register names just because the NES really doesn't have many of them, so they're not that hard to remember by number.</div>

